---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import intro from "../../public/intro.jpg";
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
---

<Layout title="Welcome to Astro.">
	<main>
		<div class="hero min-h-screen bg-base-200">
			<div class="hero-content text-center">
				<div class="flex items-center flex-col">
					<h1 class="text-5xl font-bold mb-10">“Prepare to Be Amazed!”</h1><br/>
					<Image src={intro} width={400} alt="Intro"/>
					<p class="py-6">
						📸 Dive into the cosmos with our mind-blowing collection of jaw-dropping space and NASA photos! <br/><br/>

						🌠 From distant galaxies to our very own solar system, these captivating images will leave you in awe. 🌟<br/><br/>

						🔭 Witness the Unseen: Behold stunning nebulae, mysterious black holes, and otherworldly star clusters captured by cutting-edge telescopes. 🌌<br/><br/>

						🌎 Earth from Above: Marvel at our beautiful blue planet as seen from the International Space Station. 🌏<br/><br/>

						📸 NASA’s Hidden Gems: Explore historic snapshots, behind-the-scenes glimpses, and awe-inspiring moments that define our cosmic journey. 📷<br/><br/>

						Ready to embark on an interstellar adventure? Click here to explore the universe through our lens! 🌠🔍<br/>
					</p>
					<a class="btn btn-secondary" href="/search">Let's GO!!!</a>

				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</main>
</Layout>

